1) Write a Python Program to Calculate the Area of a Rectangle and Circle.
import math

length = float(input("Enter the length of the rectangle: "))
width = float(input("Enter the width of the rectangle: "))
rectangle_area = length * width
print("Area of Rectangle =", rectangle_area)
radius = float(input("Enter the radius of the circle: "))
circle_area = math.pi * radius * radius
print("Area of Circle =", circle_area)

2) Write a Python program to Remove duplicate characters and Vowels from a 
string and display the modified string.

string = input("Enter a string: ")
vowels = "aeiouAEIOU"
result = ""
seen = set()
for char in string:
 if char not in vowels and char not in seen:
 result += char
seen.add(char)
